WEBVTT

01:37.039 --> 01:40.979
[The Best Thing]

01:41.380 --> 01:45.759
[Episode 6: Artemisia argyi, Bitter, Pungent, and Warm;
It Warms the Meridians, Stops Bleeding, and Relieves Pain]

02:00.920 --> 02:02.560
Miss Shen, wh-what's wrong?

02:02.560 --> 02:03.730
Miss Shen, are you alright?

02:03.840 --> 02:04.270
Are you...

02:07.200 --> 02:07.840
Are you...

02:07.860 --> 02:08.539
Are you okay?

02:09.030 --> 02:09.430
Are you...

02:09.449 --> 02:10.800
Are you feeling unwell?

02:12.400 --> 02:13.120
What heppened?

02:14.400 --> 02:15.240
Dr. He.

02:15.900 --> 02:17.579
My stomach hurts.

02:18.820 --> 02:19.660
Stomach pain?

02:19.980 --> 02:20.820
Is it menstrual cramps?

02:23.079 --> 02:24.010
Did you take painkillers?

02:24.620 --> 02:25.740
I did.

02:26.310 --> 02:27.470
It seems like the painkillers didn't work.

02:28.320 --> 02:28.720
Come on.

02:28.740 --> 02:29.970
I'll take you for a check-up.

02:30.700 --> 02:31.329
Be careful.

02:31.360 --> 02:32.210
I've got you.

02:32.960 --> 02:33.579
Take it slow.

02:33.600 --> 02:34.160
Let's go.

02:50.200 --> 02:51.880
Lie down, I'll do some moxibustion on you.

02:55.710 --> 02:57.190
Is it okay if I sit?

02:57.960 --> 02:58.840
What's wrong?

03:01.280 --> 03:02.920
I'm worried I might leak my period...

03:03.450 --> 03:04.480
on the sheet.

03:05.150 --> 03:06.500
Oh, I thought it was something else.

03:07.010 --> 03:09.520
Don't worry, I've got disposable sheets on the bed.

03:11.060 --> 03:12.460
It's just your pants...

03:14.190 --> 03:16.470
I'll get you a jacket to cover up later.

03:18.810 --> 03:19.970
If you don't do moxibustion,

03:20.000 --> 03:21.430
are you just gonna suffer the cramps all night?

03:27.400 --> 03:28.120
Lie down.

03:38.180 --> 03:39.610
Let me check you out.

03:55.820 --> 03:57.150
What happened today?

03:57.170 --> 03:58.170
You caught a chill.

03:58.430 --> 03:59.480
Your belly is so cold.

04:08.200 --> 04:09.350
I'll do moxibustion for you.

04:29.410 --> 04:32.560
♫A light scent♫

04:37.020 --> 04:41.270
♫Slowly awakening my heart♫

04:41.760 --> 04:45.930
♫The elusive little mist appears and disappears♫

04:46.850 --> 04:53.430
♫Quietly entering your world, your memories♫

04:54.800 --> 04:57.680
♫The unexpected encounter with the wind♫

05:00.620 --> 05:05.220
♫Layer by layer, rendering the air♫

05:02.190 --> 05:03.630
Do you feel the warmth?

05:07.000 --> 05:08.030
If the temperature isn't right,

05:07.050 --> 05:11.400
♫The whispers that are sometimes far, sometimes near♫

05:08.030 --> 05:09.070
you need to tell me, okay?

05:11.390 --> 05:12.160
Okay.

05:12.010 --> 05:17.400
♫Exchanging our hidden secrets♫

05:19.020 --> 05:24.240
♫Using my breath♫

05:25.200 --> 05:31.340
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

05:31.490 --> 05:34.060
♫To merge in♫

05:42.440 --> 05:44.750
I didn't know you had period cramps.

05:45.250 --> 05:46.570
When I checked your pulse,

05:46.590 --> 05:48.390
I didn't notice any cramp problems either.

05:48.690 --> 05:49.520
What's going on?

05:58.190 --> 06:00.670
Don't be shy about your period and not talk about it.

06:01.120 --> 06:03.270
Having a regular cycle

06:03.270 --> 06:05.310
is really important for women's health.

06:05.750 --> 06:07.080
I told you

06:07.510 --> 06:08.510
not to drink cold stuff,

06:08.510 --> 06:09.360
but you didn't listen.

06:12.830 --> 06:14.040
Actually...

06:16.050 --> 06:18.680
actually, I didn't get cramps before.

06:28.350 --> 06:29.600
Did you get caught in the rain today?

06:37.950 --> 06:38.740
What's wrong?

06:42.040 --> 06:42.920
It's just that...

06:43.960 --> 06:45.790
when I'm on my period,

06:46.659 --> 06:48.340
my emotions are all over the place.

06:52.190 --> 06:54.270
Sorry, I need to cry for a minute.

08:06.230 --> 08:07.990
How are you feeling? Are you feeling better?

08:08.870 --> 08:09.750
Much better.

08:09.830 --> 08:11.090
My belly doesn't hurt as much.

08:11.810 --> 08:12.520
Good to know.

08:13.290 --> 08:14.260
This is my shirt.

08:14.290 --> 08:15.200
You can put it on first.

08:15.710 --> 08:16.780
It can cover you up

08:16.800 --> 08:17.800
and also keep you warm.

08:18.080 --> 08:19.920
It's probably a bit chilly outside now.

08:20.760 --> 08:21.150
Okay.

08:21.470 --> 08:23.140
Well, after I'm done,

08:23.270 --> 08:24.310
I'll wash it and give it back.

08:24.920 --> 08:25.510
Okay.

08:27.600 --> 08:29.040
The moxibustion

08:29.040 --> 08:30.210
needs a bit more time to fully take effect.

08:30.230 --> 08:32.240
If you're free after work these next couple days,

08:32.270 --> 08:33.500
you can come back for a few more sessions.

08:34.200 --> 08:34.630
Okay.

08:35.100 --> 08:36.500
Don't rush to shower when you get home.

08:36.870 --> 08:38.110
The mugwort smell will linger for a while,

08:38.130 --> 08:39.200
just bear with it for now.

08:41.549 --> 08:42.340
Got it.

08:56.600 --> 08:57.600
You should go home first.

08:57.620 --> 08:59.140
Your parents must be worried about you.

09:08.960 --> 09:09.910
Dr. He,

09:10.280 --> 09:11.470
how about I wait for you

09:11.490 --> 09:12.390
and we can leave together?

09:15.010 --> 09:16.050
I need to tidy up for a while.

09:16.080 --> 09:16.960
You go ahead.

09:20.570 --> 09:21.060
Okay.

09:21.550 --> 09:22.750
Thank you then.

09:23.230 --> 09:24.130
You're welcome.

10:10.940 --> 10:12.300
You're feeling so down.

10:13.700 --> 10:15.300
Are you still not over the breakup yet?

12:12.200 --> 12:14.600
Here, Ms. Shen, have some of this.

12:16.440 --> 12:18.280
I don't want to drink it. I can't drink anymore.

12:18.320 --> 12:19.550
I made this especially for you.

12:19.550 --> 12:20.440
You're so weak today.

12:20.440 --> 12:21.440
Have some brown sugar water.

12:21.440 --> 12:21.910
It's good for your blood.

12:21.910 --> 12:22.960
Do you know that?

12:22.960 --> 12:23.630
Come on, take a sip.

12:23.630 --> 12:24.320
Just one sip.

12:29.860 --> 12:30.620
This...

12:31.630 --> 12:32.750
This isn't mine.

12:32.750 --> 12:34.010
She brought it back.

12:35.790 --> 12:36.880
What should we do then?

12:38.080 --> 12:39.000
No, no, no.

12:39.000 --> 12:40.030
Just play along with me.

12:42.960 --> 12:43.840
Well...

12:43.840 --> 12:46.480
This shirt is...

12:47.030 --> 12:48.630
Oversize!

12:49.910 --> 12:51.030
Your English is so good.

12:52.080 --> 12:53.670
Someone gave this to me.

12:53.670 --> 12:55.480
Didn't I get my pants dirty?

12:55.480 --> 12:56.840
So he just gave it to me to cover up.

12:56.860 --> 12:57.870
That TCM doctor?

13:01.150 --> 13:01.630
Ms. Shen.

13:02.630 --> 13:04.510
Last time, you insisted

13:04.510 --> 13:05.750
that you weren't familiar with that doctor.

13:06.630 --> 13:08.480
We really aren't familiar with each other.

13:08.480 --> 13:10.840
He was just being nice,

13:10.840 --> 13:11.960
I got my period on my pants,

13:11.960 --> 13:13.550
and he covered me up so I wouldn't be embarrassed.

13:14.260 --> 13:15.140
What does he look like?

13:17.320 --> 13:19.550
Just an average-looking guy.

13:19.580 --> 13:21.440
You even called Lin an average-looking guy.

13:21.440 --> 13:22.720
But I think he's quite handsome.

13:22.720 --> 13:23.360
Is he handsome?

13:23.360 --> 13:23.960
Handsome.

13:26.910 --> 13:27.630
Where's the photo?

13:27.840 --> 13:28.790
Where's the photo?

13:30.750 --> 13:32.430
I don't have his photo.

13:35.950 --> 13:36.810
I mean it.

13:38.760 --> 13:39.890
Alright, alright.

13:39.920 --> 13:41.310
I'm not feeling well today.

13:41.330 --> 13:43.180
I'm going to bed now.

13:43.330 --> 13:45.040
I'll take a shower when I wake up tomorrow morning.

13:46.090 --> 13:48.210
Are you sure you can fall asleep this early?

13:49.510 --> 13:50.840
Yeah, I'm sure.

13:50.840 --> 13:51.480
I'm so sleepy.

13:53.030 --> 13:53.910
Come on, come on.

13:54.120 --> 13:55.080
I'm going to sleep.

13:55.080 --> 13:55.960
Fine.

13:58.440 --> 13:59.360
There's something fishy about it.

14:00.840 --> 14:02.120
That shirt looks nice,

14:02.120 --> 14:03.230
buy one for me, okay?

14:03.360 --> 14:04.640
Do you want to wear a matching shirt with him?

14:04.720 --> 14:05.840
Hey, watch it!

15:24.520 --> 15:27.400
His Moments are all about TCM!

15:43.810 --> 15:45.240
His photos give off such a stereotypically guy vibe.

16:04.960 --> 16:05.750
Hold on.

16:19.130 --> 16:20.890
Why am I feeling guilty?

16:34.600 --> 16:35.910
I should like a few more posts instead.

16:37.840 --> 16:38.670
This one.

16:42.610 --> 16:43.180
That's right.

16:43.580 --> 16:44.300
This one.

17:42.200 --> 17:43.070
Still not sleeping?

17:51.290 --> 17:53.290
I'm about to sleep.

18:04.270 --> 18:04.790
Didn't you see

18:04.790 --> 18:06.830
the health article I shared?

18:07.020 --> 18:09.020
It says people need to sleep before 11 PM.

18:09.350 --> 18:12.070
No phones before bed, and stay calm.

18:13.640 --> 18:14.400
Article?

18:14.970 --> 18:15.920
What article?

18:19.400 --> 18:21.270
WeChat moments?

18:26.350 --> 18:27.740
I saw it.

18:27.770 --> 18:29.770
So I'm about to sleep.

18:38.680 --> 18:40.110
Your reading skills are great.

18:40.110 --> 18:41.790
You read seven or eight articles in a minute.

18:42.070 --> 18:43.270
And you absorbed them all.

18:43.440 --> 18:44.640
Speed-reader, huh?

18:46.140 --> 18:47.720
Those likes...

18:48.830 --> 18:50.350
I'm doomed!

18:52.160 --> 18:53.270
Aha.

19:24.230 --> 19:26.320
Brown sugar ginger bubble tea.

19:26.960 --> 19:27.830
Didn't you drink enough Chinese medicine?

19:27.830 --> 19:29.200
Now you're even drinking healthy bubble tea.

19:29.720 --> 19:31.720
I'm on my period and my belly hurts.

19:33.750 --> 19:35.480
You never cared before.

19:37.270 --> 19:39.030
Yesterday was day one,

19:39.030 --> 19:41.400
and I wasn't feeling well
so I went to Dr. He for moxibustion.

19:41.400 --> 19:42.550
He urged me to keep that in mind.

19:43.590 --> 19:45.960
This doctor is really responsible, isn't he?

19:48.200 --> 19:49.160
Oh, right, Xiangya.

19:49.160 --> 19:50.240
Open your phone,

19:50.240 --> 19:51.320
and I want to test a feature with you.

19:51.640 --> 19:52.070
What's up?

19:52.070 --> 19:52.920
See,

19:52.920 --> 19:54.070
if I accidentally

19:54.070 --> 19:55.590
like your post on Moments

19:55.590 --> 19:56.640
and unlike it right away,

19:56.640 --> 19:57.680
do you still get a notification?

19:58.000 --> 19:58.720
Yeah!

19:59.240 --> 20:01.420
I've used this move on a bunch of dudes.

20:01.920 --> 20:02.850
Ah?

20:03.880 --> 20:05.240
Then I guessed right.

20:05.440 --> 20:08.010
Yesterday I liked Dr. He's post and then unliked it.

20:08.160 --> 20:10.130
To make it look casual, I liked a few more posts.

20:10.160 --> 20:11.400
But he found out.

20:11.440 --> 20:12.830
I was totally caught red-handed.

20:12.830 --> 20:13.830
I'm so doomed.

20:14.720 --> 20:15.790
What's the big deal?

20:15.790 --> 20:17.400
Just say it to him directly

20:17.590 --> 20:18.440
that you're curious about him

20:18.440 --> 20:19.830
and want to see his Moments.
What's wrong with that?

20:20.830 --> 20:21.590
Let me see your chat history.

20:21.590 --> 20:22.920
I'll give you some advice.

20:22.920 --> 20:23.790
It's that one.

20:29.480 --> 20:30.350
Lin Yishen.

20:30.750 --> 20:32.070
From a guy's perspective,

20:32.070 --> 20:33.240
do you think there's a chance here?

20:33.240 --> 20:33.920
Let me see.

20:35.400 --> 20:37.590
At 11:45 PM,

20:38.090 --> 20:39.810
he asked, "Still not sleeping?"

20:42.480 --> 20:43.270
There's a chance.

20:45.350 --> 20:46.350
How so?

20:46.720 --> 20:48.440
Do you think a guy would care

20:48.440 --> 20:50.000
when a girl he's not interested in

20:50.000 --> 20:51.200
goes to sleep?

20:53.110 --> 20:55.000
But he's my doctor,

20:55.000 --> 20:56.710
and he's treating my insomnia,

20:56.880 --> 20:58.240
of course he'd care when I go to sleep.

20:58.550 --> 20:59.440
Yeah, yeah.

21:00.920 --> 21:02.240
Just as I expected.

21:02.240 --> 21:03.510
He's a boring old scholar.

21:06.750 --> 21:07.920
Weren't you

21:07.920 --> 21:09.200
drinking that licorice water a while ago?

21:11.030 --> 21:12.750
He barely posts on Moments.

21:12.750 --> 21:15.000
Look, he posted one about licorice.

21:16.480 --> 21:18.350
He told me about the licorice water,

21:18.480 --> 21:20.000
so of course he had to teach me how to drink it, right?

21:22.790 --> 21:25.480
This hot TCM doctor is such a player.

21:25.750 --> 21:27.270
He posted it on Moments on purpose

21:27.270 --> 21:28.400
waiting for you to like it,

21:28.400 --> 21:30.000
and he could chat with you.

21:30.000 --> 21:32.000
But it turns out, he posted it months ago,

21:32.000 --> 21:32.970
and you only liked it just now.

21:33.640 --> 21:35.880
Honestly, I think he should just be more straightforward.

21:36.200 --> 21:37.000
Didn't you say

21:37.000 --> 21:38.460
that he's nice, great,

21:38.830 --> 21:40.030
handsome and gentle?

21:40.030 --> 21:41.590
And he even supports your plan to study abroad!

21:42.090 --> 21:43.920
He can do things that Yan Heng couldn't do.

21:43.920 --> 21:44.960
Why don't you give him a chance?

21:45.160 --> 21:47.270
How can he be the same as Yan Heng?

21:47.270 --> 21:48.620
He's my friend.

21:48.640 --> 21:49.720
You two are also my friends.

21:49.720 --> 21:50.920
You both support me too, right?

21:52.590 --> 21:54.180
Well, we are us.

21:54.510 --> 21:55.750
But that TCM doctor is a guy!

21:55.750 --> 21:56.510
That's different.

21:56.510 --> 21:57.750
Am I not a guy?

21:59.790 --> 22:01.590
We've known each other for a long time.

22:01.590 --> 22:02.790
But Dr. He is different.

22:02.790 --> 22:04.640
No matter how long we've known each other, I'm still a guy.

22:04.640 --> 22:05.510
Shut up.

22:05.510 --> 22:06.270
I won't.

22:06.270 --> 22:07.480
Alright, stop fighting.

22:11.000 --> 22:13.370
Poor hot TCM doctor.

22:13.390 --> 22:15.460
The guy has feelings, but the girl does not.

22:57.490 --> 22:59.040
[Brown sugar ginger bubble tea]

23:04.110 --> 23:05.440
Try not to eat ginger in autumn,

23:05.700 --> 23:08.190
or it'll make the dryness worse.

24:41.520 --> 24:48.840
[Ingredients for duck with dried tangerine peel soup]

24:49.740 --> 25:02.480
[Ingredients and recipe for ginseng and lotus seed soup]

25:42.600 --> 25:44.400
Here are some medicinal food recipes.

25:44.480 --> 25:46.240
You can try them when cooking.

26:02.830 --> 26:03.510
Thank you.

26:06.680 --> 26:09.160
But why did you suddenly send me this?

26:21.550 --> 26:23.070
I saw your Moments.

26:23.400 --> 26:25.750
Try not to eat ginger in autumn,
or it could make the dryness worse.

26:28.030 --> 26:32.310
At 11:45 PM, he asked, "Still not sleeping?"

26:32.830 --> 26:34.480
Do you think a man would care

26:34.480 --> 26:36.030
when a girl he's not interested in

26:36.030 --> 26:37.110
goes to sleep?

26:37.440 --> 26:39.130
He barely posts on Moments.

26:39.150 --> 26:41.630
Look, he posted something about licorice.

26:41.680 --> 26:44.440
This handsome TCM doctor is such a player.

26:44.680 --> 26:46.350
He posted it on Moments on purpose

26:46.350 --> 26:47.240
waiting for you to like it,

26:47.240 --> 26:48.350
and he could chat with you.

26:48.350 --> 26:49.270
But it turns out,

26:49.270 --> 26:50.440
he posted it months ago,

26:50.440 --> 26:51.550
and you only liked it just now.

26:51.550 --> 26:54.030
Honestly, I think he should just be more direct.

27:05.680 --> 27:06.550
Okay.

27:07.350 --> 27:09.500
Looks like you've been keeping a close eye on my Moments.

27:19.240 --> 27:21.750
But the ginger in the bubble tea doesn't really count.

27:23.000 --> 27:25.750
Can my family members try these recipes?

27:26.110 --> 27:27.700
My father has hypertension,

27:27.720 --> 27:29.270
and my mother is quite healthy.

27:46.590 --> 27:47.390
Yes, they can.

27:47.480 --> 27:49.750
Medicinal food is mild. Everyone can eat it.

27:55.940 --> 27:56.940
Thank you, Dr. He.

28:06.680 --> 28:07.440
You're welcome.

28:19.930 --> 28:21.540
Why am I overthinking it?

28:23.160 --> 28:24.160
I'm just making things up in my head.

29:32.060 --> 29:34.940
Mom!

29:34.960 --> 29:35.460
Doc-

29:35.480 --> 29:35.920
What's wrong?

29:35.920 --> 29:36.310
Doctor!

29:36.310 --> 29:38.640
Please check what's wrong with my mom quickly!

29:40.720 --> 29:41.670
Mom!

29:41.830 --> 29:43.480
Mom, wake up!

29:44.830 --> 29:45.480
Mom!

29:47.400 --> 29:48.590
Open the IV line.

29:48.590 --> 29:50.400
Prepare one set of respiratory stimulants
and one set of blood pressure medications.

29:50.400 --> 29:51.070
Go prepare them quickly.

29:51.070 --> 29:51.680
Okay.

29:52.110 --> 29:53.030
You stay here, I'll go prepare.

29:53.030 --> 29:54.200
Mom!

29:54.200 --> 29:55.200
What's wrong?

29:55.200 --> 29:56.070
Don't panic.

29:56.070 --> 29:57.030
Come here.

29:59.520 --> 30:00.520
Don't be sad, don't panic.

30:01.000 --> 30:01.960
The patient

30:01.960 --> 30:02.920
has brain metastasis,

30:02.920 --> 30:04.550
pressing on the vital center.

30:04.840 --> 30:06.310
It's not looking good.

30:06.550 --> 30:08.110
She needs to be transferred to ICU

30:08.110 --> 30:09.480
for invasive treatment immediately.

30:12.290 --> 30:13.370
Invasive?

30:13.400 --> 30:14.120
Yes.

30:14.640 --> 30:15.990
The situation is very urgent.

30:16.070 --> 30:18.000
We must perform a tracheostomy and cardiac pacing.

30:23.070 --> 30:24.030
Doctor...

30:26.240 --> 30:27.240
No, no.

30:27.350 --> 30:29.740
My mom has been through enough,

30:30.110 --> 30:31.030
please don't make her suffer more.

30:31.030 --> 30:32.310
This is the most effective method.

30:32.310 --> 30:35.160
No, we're not doing this surgery.

30:35.160 --> 30:36.550
But this is the only chance.

30:36.550 --> 30:37.400
It's too painful!

30:37.400 --> 30:38.060
Doctor...

30:38.720 --> 30:39.270
Doctor,

30:39.270 --> 30:41.000
can you think of a way

30:41.510 --> 30:43.830
to buy some time for my mom?

30:43.830 --> 30:46.070
I want my family to see her one last time.

30:46.070 --> 30:47.310
Please.

30:47.640 --> 30:50.030
Can you help me find a way?

30:50.790 --> 30:51.440
Alright.

30:52.250 --> 30:53.140
I'll do my best.

30:53.170 --> 30:54.570
Okay, thank you.

30:55.850 --> 30:59.440
Mom, please hang in there.

31:15.590 --> 31:16.440
Mom!

31:18.550 --> 31:19.310
Mr. He.

31:19.440 --> 31:20.530
Are you sure you want to give up?

31:21.480 --> 31:22.960
The tumor has already spread.

31:23.680 --> 31:26.410
Her respiratory and cardiac functions have been affected.

31:27.800 --> 31:29.880
There's no point in rescuing her.

31:31.040 --> 31:32.130
Let her go.

32:10.030 --> 32:10.830
Dr. He.

32:14.880 --> 32:15.720
Why are you here?

32:15.720 --> 32:16.920
I'm here to buy some food.

32:16.920 --> 32:18.110
You're eating too?

32:27.400 --> 32:30.590
Why do you look so down?

32:34.350 --> 32:35.110
Not really.

32:36.000 --> 32:37.310
I'm just eating.

32:40.440 --> 32:41.490
Did...

32:41.710 --> 32:43.510
did something happen?

